Individual




William F. Susetka



Mr. William F. Susetka is Independent Director at Helen of Troy Ltd. He is on the Board of Directors at Helen of Troy Ltd. and Ladies Professional Golf Association.
Mr. Susetka was previously employed as Chief Operating Officer by Nice-Pak Products, Inc., President-Global Marketing by Avon Products, Inc., and President-Retail Division by Clairol, Inc. He also served on the board at Avon Foundation, Cosmetics Toiletry & Fragrance Association, and Personal Care Products Council.



